[{"Code":"en","Title":"Overview","Slug":"product-overview-3","ContentType":2,"Content":"<blockquote style=\"background:#fdf2ce;border-left:4px solid #7f6416;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mdirszr6-8n1saa-005\" class=\"warningBox\" data-background=\"#fdf2ce\" data-border=\"#7f6416\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mdirt4ou-nly321-008\">Pilot Feature Notice</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mdirszr6-b183yr-006\">Bill payments is currently in pilot phase.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"e355563b-e19e-4c1c-80ec-31ea14969926\"><strong>Xendit Bill Payments</strong> enables merchants to facilitate various bill payment services through a single API integration. This service allows your end users to pay utility bills, purchase prepaid services, and make regular payments all within your application or platform.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"d5a7bc10-5e7f-4575-a146-666448954687\">What are Bill Payments?</h3><p data-block-id=\"0e253919-5bf3-4f30-b26e-e617db79c51c\">Bill Payments is a digital service that lets people pay their bills and make purchases electronically. Think of it as a digital payment counter where your users can handle multiple types of payments in one place. In Indonesia, this service is commonly known as PPOB (Payment Point Online Banks).</p><p data-block-id=\"08eec1ed-f17e-4349-b5be-084e758e6c7f\"><strong>Common Features</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"892ca4b8-0995-4b79-8cdc-1f6cfc4c83dd\"><li data-block-id=\"8e0885c2-e8be-417f-813c-86bb8209f844\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ef000aef-809f-4234-b733-23bdd0c715f6\"><strong>Pay Utility Bills</strong>: Electricity, water, and other utility services</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bb216e52-6dac-4f3b-b316-557a1c28c3d8\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"84aa5af5-c20c-45bd-a2cf-276fc6cdde86\"><strong>Buy Prepaid Services</strong>: Phone credit top-ups, electricity tokens, internet data packages</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7a9f3949-714d-4514-b364-e294d291e051\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"d7c92c39-3a9b-42f2-931f-9d7a2499b676\"><strong>Make Regular Payments</strong>: Government taxes, insurance premiums, school fees</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"7a62ca4a-2b73-4b14-b6ca-399c79ab598a\">How It Works?</h3><p data-block-id=\"f1508a12-be8c-417b-ba72-884bb5c1cc77\"><img data-block-id=\"765f1b01-65ef-46fe-b08e-a8faa7792fe6\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(114).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><ol data-block-id=\"d537cd1e-aba3-4f19-b070-15b13c58555e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"af2e3eb2-2f22-475b-b286-f978287d36eb\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"acabeba6-b7cf-439c-8b8d-4be3bcc6b50c\"><strong>Customer provides account information</strong> - The user enters their account number (like electricity customer ID)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"49124d39-f114-4335-aaca-fcc97f2a811f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f5e3de3d-a30b-442e-b2bb-ad52ec5fbb6e\"><strong>System checks bill details</strong> - Xendit verifies the account and retrieves bill information</p></li><li data-block-id=\"24a47bef-283b-4070-bcee-1e39e1329377\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f8ac4a70-b540-4b56-8e81-e98a7548f1f0\"><strong>Customer confirms and pays</strong> - User reviews bill details and completes payment</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bfd8dfa5-3c9c-4071-b5b3-3f54a3a24eb3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"300de6cf-9e95-4e68-96ee-e868ce46a04d\"><strong>Payment is processed</strong> - Transaction is executed immediately</p></li><li data-block-id=\"98013e39-c4f4-4b24-a43b-8d8cd88dc9e3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"247409b0-2707-46ae-8ede-1800278e4937\"><strong>Customer receives notification</strong> - Confirmation of successful payment is sent</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"a88aa077-770f-4ec4-89c4-5f69f5a2e063\">Instead of visiting multiple service offices to pay different bills, your users can complete all their payments through your platform with Xendit Bill Payments.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"70035706-df2a-4648-a9c6-49b97f2392c4\">Supported Products</h3><p data-block-id=\"2523c633-4f53-4556-b0f0-de57ba7c9596\">Currently, Xendit Bill Payments supports:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"912\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:912px;width:912px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:304px;\"><col style=\"width:304px;\"><col style=\"width:304px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"2d80a402-be6b-44b9-b9a1-d3b578df5cff\">Category</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"ff24f8e2-2094-419a-9b04-b93a0336caf5\">Products</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"2df2fda0-f2c3-4219-aadc-e0b6d88e0cec\">Status</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"d057440e-d73c-4875-b54e-6da9513fb970\">Utilities</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"50c9bda5-faad-4a8b-b73a-e34d957365ab\">Electricity - PLN</p><ul data-block-id=\"e2f87cb3-f66a-4667-95ed-0d074bdc38c2\"><li data-block-id=\"0745468d-7ea5-441b-96fb-6e8791a234a4\"><p data-block-id=\"42887853-e5b1-4fce-81bb-9d0675c1d5ea\">Prepaid</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c6310c51-1b26-4afa-95ef-192d351c38cf\"><p data-block-id=\"5b365676-68ac-4650-a02a-e8c65662f646\">Postpaid</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"94137d3f-16d3-4e80-9b9b-ae73ef6ddd1d\">Live</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"049d61dc-855e-4096-ac1f-f2377a5a2583\">Water</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"44a2dd23-d923-4c37-a1a9-83c70173f0c3\">Various PDAMs</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"37470440-a494-4576-bfeb-3e4d135a07bb\">Coming Soon</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"00cd7eb9-134e-4c34-a4b2-60190ae6ec13\">Telco</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"8a948477-a272-433a-afd6-80e5bf7d4477\">Phone and internet providers</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"faaf541a-5818-4637-a951-e856d9107093\">Coming Soon</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"5e5938e4-88c9-4984-a5b4-7a85c418e086\">Entertainment</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"deacdcff-8df5-4711-900d-22a9972fc5da\">Streaming and content services</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"5b3faff2-adab-46a5-be43-0f635d47485f\">Coming Soon</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"08c6c5c4-d7ac-40ea-95ba-700657d1d0e5\">Financial Institutions</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"0643a35d-e503-4ccc-9482-72fd47031a60\">Banking and financial services</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"0330532d-8c22-4f48-9cbd-74247b4bad06\">Coming Soon</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"a2961257-ce66-49d0-824e-68aed660c574\">Tax</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"738b8a26-4b6a-4495-9f5e-59af0af4e643\">Government tax payments</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"1be994ad-d1a8-4321-a168-c88394272d25\">Coming Soon</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"31197f7e-7b16-4627-9716-e1b5aa933c66\">Why Xendit Bill Payments?</h3><ul data-block-id=\"97ddb4ff-b657-4191-b82a-5dbf6e4bd5e9\"><li data-block-id=\"ff1e12b3-66c4-41d4-8326-639da47aa457\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"678c2e8f-df1f-462e-8d26-787f7b9b5fb8\"><strong>One Integration, Regional Reach</strong>: Single integration for bill payments across countries.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c376d33a-b16a-4fc5-b15e-792162cb4b14\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"67035966-5d10-4ac4-a885-d81fdeae2c2c\"><strong>Attractive Commercial Terms</strong>: Process bill payments and collect funds through Xendit's payment methods with zero payment collection fees (for selected payment methods), complemented by bill payment revenue.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bbb4cf3c-1e5f-4f3e-b71e-7ec0a74c265c\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"d873ddb0-a914-40c0-a2fb-fb81b0ac13e5\"><strong>Leverage Xendit's Ecosystem</strong>: Access comprehensive features from Xendit's payment gateway ecosystem - unified reporting, billing, instant notifications, and reliable uptime backed by 24/7 support.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"5fd9c6c0-3ef2-405b-bf03-e857820e4109\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Overview","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Gambaran Umum","Slug":"product-overview-3","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#fdf2ce;border-left:4px solid #7f6416;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mdirszr6-8n1saa-005\" class=\"warningBox\" data-background=\"#fdf2ce\" data-border=\"#7f6416\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mdirt4ou-nly321-008\">Pemberitahuan Fitur Pilot</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mdirszr6-b183yr-006\">Pembayaran tagihan saat ini dalam tahap pilot.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"e355563b-e19e-4c1c-80ec-31ea14969926\"><strong>Xendit Bill Payments</strong> memungkinkan merchant untuk memfasilitasi berbagai layanan pembayaran tagihan melalui satu integrasi API. Layanan ini memungkinkan pengguna akhir Anda untuk membayar tagihan utilitas, membeli layanan prabayar, dan melakukan pembayaran rutin semua dalam aplikasi atau platform Anda.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"d5a7bc10-5e7f-4575-a146-666448954687\">Apa itu Pembayaran Tagihan?</h3><p data-block-id=\"0e253919-5bf3-4f30-b26e-e617db79c51c\">Pembayaran Tagihan adalah layanan digital yang memungkinkan orang membayar tagihan dan melakukan pembelian secara elektronik. Anggap saja ini sebagai loket pembayaran digital di mana pengguna Anda dapat menangani berbagai jenis pembayaran di satu tempat. Di Indonesia, layanan ini umumnya dikenal sebagai PPOB (Payment Point Online Banks).</p><p data-block-id=\"08eec1ed-f17e-4349-b5be-084e758e6c7f\"><strong>Fitur Umum</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"892ca4b8-0995-4b79-8cdc-1f6cfc4c83dd\"><li data-block-id=\"8e0885c2-e8be-417f-813c-86bb8209f844\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ef000aef-809f-4234-b733-23bdd0c715f6\"><strong>Bayar Tagihan Utilitas</strong>: Listrik, air, dan layanan utilitas lainnya</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bb216e52-6dac-4f3b-b316-557a1c28c3d8\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"84aa5af5-c20c-45bd-a2cf-276fc6cdde86\"><strong>Beli Layanan Prabayar</strong>: Isi ulang pulsa telepon, token listrik, paket data internet</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7a9f3949-714d-4514-b364-e294d291e051\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"d7c92c39-3a9b-42f2-931f-9d7a2499b676\"><strong>Lakukan Pembayaran Rutin</strong>: Pajak pemerintah, premi asuransi, biaya sekolah</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"7a62ca4a-2b73-4b14-b6ca-399c79ab598a\">Bagaimana Cara Kerjanya?</h3><p data-block-id=\"f1508a12-be8c-417b-ba72-884bb5c1cc77\"><img data-block-id=\"765f1b01-65ef-46fe-b08e-a8faa7792fe6\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(114).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><ol data-block-id=\"d537cd1e-aba3-4f19-b070-15b13c58555e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"af2e3eb2-2f22-475b-b286-f978287d36eb\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"acabeba6-b7cf-439c-8b8d-4be3bcc6b50c\"><strong>Pelanggan memberikan informasi akun</strong> - Pengguna memasukkan nomor akun mereka (seperti ID pelanggan listrik)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"49124d39-f114-4335-aaca-fcc97f2a811f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f5e3de3d-a30b-442e-b2bb-ad52ec5fbb6e\"><strong>Sistem memeriksa detail tagihan</strong> - Xendit memverifikasi akun dan mengambil informasi tagihan</p></li><li data-block-id=\"24a47bef-283b-4070-bcee-1e39e1329377\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f8ac4a70-b540-4b56-8e81-e98a7548f1f0\"><strong>Pelanggan mengonfirmasi dan membayar</strong> - Pengguna meninjau detail tagihan dan menyelesaikan pembayaran</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bfd8dfa5-3c9c-4071-b5b3-3f54a3a24eb3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"300de6cf-9e95-4e68-96ee-e868ce46a04d\"><strong>Pembayaran diproses</strong> - Transaksi dieksekusi segera</p></li><li data-block-id=\"98013e39-c4f4-4b24-a43b-8d8cd88dc9e3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"247409b0-2707-46ae-8ede-1800278e4937\"><strong>Pelanggan menerima notifikasi</strong> - Konfirmasi pembayaran yang berhasil dikirim</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"a88aa077-770f-4ec4-89c4-5f69f5a2e063\">Daripada mengunjungi beberapa kantor layanan untuk membayar tagihan yang berbeda, pengguna Anda dapat menyelesaikan semua pembayaran mereka melalui platform Anda dengan Xendit Bill Payments.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"70035706-df2a-4648-a9c6-49b97f2392c4\">Produk yang Didukung</h3><p data-block-id=\"2523c633-4f53-4556-b0f0-de57ba7c9596\">Saat ini, Xendit Bill Payments mendukung:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"912\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:912px;width:912px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:304px;\"><col style=\"width:304px;\"><col style=\"width:304px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"2d80a402-be6b-44b9-b9a1-d3b578df5cff\">Kategori</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"ff24f8e2-2094-419a-9b04-b93a0336caf5\">Produk</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"2df2fda0-f2c3-4219-aadc-e0b6d88e0cec\">Status</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"d057440e-d73c-4875-b54e-6da9513fb970\">Utilitas</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"50c9bda5-faad-4a8b-b73a-e34d957365ab\">Listrik - PLN</p><ul data-block-id=\"e2f87cb3-f66a-4667-95ed-0d074bdc38c2\"><li data-block-id=\"0745468d-7ea5-441b-96fb-6e8791a234a4\"><p data-block-id=\"42887853-e5b1-4fce-81bb-9d0675c1d5ea\">Prabayar</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c6310c51-1b26-4afa-95ef-192d351c38cf\"><p data-block-id=\"5b365676-68ac-4650-a02a-e8c65662f646\">Pascabayar</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"94137d3f-16d3-4e80-9b9b-ae73ef6ddd1d\">Tersedia</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"049d61dc-855e-4096-ac1f-f2377a5a2583\">Air</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"44a2dd23-d923-4c37-a1a9-83c70173f0c3\">Berbagai PDAM</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"37470440-a494-4576-bfeb-3e4d135a07bb\">Segera Hadir</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"00cd7eb9-134e-4c34-a4b2-60190ae6ec13\">Telco</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"8a948477-a272-433a-afd6-80e5bf7d4477\">Penyedia telepon dan internet</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"faaf541a-5818-4637-a951-e856d9107093\">Segera Hadir</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"5e5938e4-88c9-4984-a5b4-7a85c418e086\">Hiburan</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"deacdcff-8df5-4711-900d-22a9972fc5da\">Layanan streaming dan konten</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"5b3faff2-adab-46a5-be43-0f635d47485f\">Segera Hadir</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"08c6c5c4-d7ac-40ea-95ba-7006571d0e5\">Lembaga Keuangan</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"0643a35d-e503-4ccc-9482-72fd47031a60\">Layanan perbankan dan keuangan</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"0330532d-8c22-4f48-9cbd-74247b4bad06\">Segera Hadir</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"a2961257-ce66-49d0-824e-68aed660c574\">Pajak</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"738b8a26-4b6a-4495-9f5e-59af0af4e643\">Pembayaran pajak pemerintah</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"1be994ad-d1a8-4321-a168-c88394272d25\">Segera Hadir</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"31197f7e-7b16-4627-9716-e1b5aa933c66\">Mengapa Menggunakan Xendit Bill Payments?</h3><ul data-block-id=\"97ddb4ff-b657-4191-b82a-5dbf6e4bd5e9\"><li data-block-id=\"ff1e12b3-66c4-41d4-8326-639da47aa457\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"678c2e8f-df1f-462e-8d26-787f7b9b5fb8\"><strong>Satu Integrasi, Jangkauan Regional</strong>: Integrasi tunggal untuk pembayaran tagihan di berbagai negara.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c376d33a-b16a-4fc5-b15e-792162cb4b14\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"67035966-5d10-4ac4-a885-d81fdeae2c2c\"><strong>Ketentuan Komersial yang Menarik</strong>: Proses pembayaran tagihan dan kumpulkan dana melalui metode pembayaran Xendit dengan biaya pengumpulan pembayaran nol (untuk metode pembayaran tertentu), dilengkapi dengan pendapatan dari pembayaran tagihan.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bbb4cf3c-1e5f-4f3e-b71e-7ec0a74c265c\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"d873ddb0-a914-40c0-a2fb-fb81b0ac13e5\"><strong>Manfaatkan Ekosistem Xendit</strong>: Akses fitur komprehensif dari ekosistem payment gateway Xendit - pelaporan terpadu, penagihan, notifikasi instan, dan waktu aktif yang andal didukung oleh dukungan 24/7.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"5fd9c6c0-3ef2-405b-bf03-e857820e4109\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Gambaran Umum","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ภาพรวม","Slug":"product-overview-3","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#fdf2ce;border-left:4px solid #7f6416;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mdirszr6-8n1saa-005\" class=\"warningBox\" data-background=\"#fdf2ce\" data-border=\"#7f6416\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mdirt4ou-nly321-008\">ประกาศคุณสมบัติช่วงนำร่อง</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mdirszr6-b183yr-006\">บริการ Bill payments กำลังอยู่ในช่วงนำร่อง</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"e355563b-e19e-4c1c-80ec-31ea14969926\"><strong>Xendit Bill Payments</strong> ช่วยให้ร้านค้าสามารถอำนวยความสะดวกในการชำระค่าบริการต่างๆ ผ่านการเชื่อมต่อ API เพียงครั้งเดียว บริการนี้ช่วยให้ผู้ใช้ปลายทางของคุณสามารถชำระค่าสาธารณูปโภค ซื้อบริการแบบเติมเงิน และชำระเงินตามกำหนดได้ทั้งหมดภายในแอปพลิเคชันหรือแพลตฟอร์มของคุณ</p><h3 data-block-id=\"d5a7bc10-5e7f-4575-a146-666448954687\">Bill Payments คืออะไร?</h3><p data-block-id=\"0e253919-5bf3-4f30-b26e-e617db79c51c\">Bill Payments คือบริการดิจิทัลที่ช่วยให้ผู้คนสามารถชำระค่าบริการและทำการซื้อสินค้าทางอิเล็กทรอนิกส์ได้ ลองนึกภาพว่าเป็นเคาน์เตอร์ชำระเงินดิจิทัลที่ผู้ใช้ของคุณสามารถจัดการการชำระเงินหลายประเภทได้ในที่เดียว ในประเทศอินโดนีเซีย บริการนี้เป็นที่รู้จักกันทั่วไปในชื่อ PPOB (Payment Point Online Banks)</p><p data-block-id=\"08eec1ed-f17e-4349-b5be-084e758e6c7f\"><strong>คุณสมบัติทั่วไป</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"892ca4b8-0995-4b79-8cdc-1f6cfc4c83dd\"><li data-block-id=\"8e0885c2-e8be-417f-813c-86bb8209f844\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ef000aef-809f-4234-b733-23bdd0c715f6\"><strong>ชำระค่าสาธารณูปโภค</strong>: ค่าไฟฟ้า ค่าน้ำ และบริการสาธารณูปโภคอื่น ๆ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bb216e52-6dac-4f3b-b316-557a1c28c3d8\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"84aa5af5-c20c-45bd-a2cf-276fc6cdde86\"><strong>ซื้อบริการแบบเติมเงิน</strong>: การเติมเงินโทรศัพท์มือถือ โทเค็นไฟฟ้า แพ็กเกจอินเทอร์เน็ต</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7a9f3949-714d-4514-b364-e294d291e051\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"d7c92c39-3a9b-42f2-931f-9d7a2499b676\"><strong>ชำระเงินตามกำหนด</strong>: ภาษีของรัฐบาล เบี้ยประกันภัย ค่าเล่าเรียน</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"7a62ca4a-2b73-4b14-b6ca-399c79ab598a\">ทำงานอย่างไร?</h3><p data-block-id=\"f1508a12-be8c-417b-ba72-884bb5c1cc77\"><img data-block-id=\"765f1b01-65ef-46fe-b08e-a8faa7792fe6\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(114).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><ol data-block-id=\"d537cd1e-aba3-4f19-b070-15b13c58555e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"af2e3eb2-f22-475b-b286-f978287d36eb\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"acabeba6-b7cf-439c-8b8d-4be3bcc6b50c\"><strong>ลูกค้าให้ข้อมูลบัญชี</strong> - ผู้ใช้ป้อนหมายเลขบัญชีของตน (เช่น รหัสลูกค้าไฟฟ้า)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"49124d39-f114-4335-aaca-fcc97f2a811f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f5e3de3d-a30b-442e-b2bb-ad52ec5fbb6e\"><strong>ระบบตรวจสอบรายละเอียดบิล</strong> - Xendit ตรวจสอบบัญชีและดึงข้อมูลบิล</p></li><li data-block-id=\"24a47bef-283b-4070-bcee-1e39e1329377\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f8ac4a70-b540-4b56-8e81-e98a7548f1f0\"><strong>ลูกค้ายืนยันและชำระเงิน</strong> - ผู้ใช้ตรวจสอบรายละเอียดบิลและดำเนินการชำระเงินให้เสร็จสมบูรณ์</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bfd8dfa5-3c9c-4071-b5b3-3f54a3a24eb3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"300de6cf-9e95-4e68-96ee-e868ce46a04d\"><strong>ดำเนินการชำระเงิน</strong> - ธุรกรรมจะถูกดำเนินการทันที</p></li><li data-block-id=\"98013e39-c4f4-4b24-a43b-8d8cd88dc9e3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"247409b0-2707-46ae-8ede-1800278e4937\"><strong>ลูกค้าได้รับการแจ้งเตือน</strong> - มีการส่งการยืนยันการชำระเงินที่สำเร็จ</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"a88aa077-770f-4ec4-89c4-5f69f5a2e063\">แทนที่จะต้องไปที่สำนักงานบริการหลายแห่งเพื่อชำระบิลที่แตกต่างกัน ผู้ใช้ของคุณสามารถดำเนินการชำระเงินทั้งหมดผ่านแพลตฟอร์มของคุณด้วย Xendit Bill Payments</p><h3 data-block-id=\"70035706-df2a-4648-a9c6-49b97f2392c4\">ผลิตภัณฑ์ที่รองรับ</h3><p data-block-id=\"2523c633-4f53-4556-b0f0-de57ba7c9596\">ปัจจุบัน Xendit Bill Payments รองรับ:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"912\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:912px;width:912px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:304px;\"><col style=\"width:304px;\"><col style=\"width:304px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"2d80a402-be6b-44b9-b9a1-d3b578df5cff\">หมวดหมู่</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"ff24f8e2-2094-419a-9b04-b93a0336caf5\">ผลิตภัณฑ์</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"2df2fda0-f2c3-4219-aadc-e0b6d88e0cec\">สถานะ</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"d057440e-d73c-4875-b54e-6da9513fb970\">สาธารณูปโภค</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"50c9bda5-faad-4a8b-b73a-e34d957365ab\">ค่าไฟฟ้า - PLN</p><ul data-block-id=\"e2f87cb3-f66a-4667-95ed-0d074bdc38c2\"><li data-block-id=\"0745468d-7ea5-441b-96fb-6e8791a234a4\"><p data-block-id=\"42887853-e5b1-4fce-81bb-9d0675c1d5ea\">แบบเติมเงิน</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c6310c51-1b26-4afa-95ef-192d351c38cf\"><p data-block-id=\"5b365676-68ac-4650-a02a-e8c65662f646\">แบบรายเดือน</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"94137d3f-16d3-4e80-9b9b-ae73ef6ddd1d\">ใช้งานจริง</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"049d61dc-855e-4096-ac1f-f2377a5a2583\">ค่าน้ำ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"44a2dd23-d923-4c37-a1a9-83c70173f0c3\">PDAMs ต่างๆ</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"37470440-a494-4576-bfeb-3e4d135a07bb\">เร็วๆ นี้</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"00cd7eb9-134e-4c34-a4b2-60190ae6ec13\">โทรคมนาคม</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"8a948477-a272-433a-afd6-80e5bf7d4477\">ผู้ให้บริการโทรศัพท์และอินเทอร์เน็ต</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"faaf541a-5818-4637-a951-e856d9107093\">เร็วๆ นี้</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"5e5938e4-88c9-4984-a5b4-7a85c418e086\">ความบันเทิง</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"deacdcff-8df5-4711-900d-22a9972fc5da\">บริการสตรีมมิ่งและเนื้อหา</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"5b3faff2-adab-46a5-be43-0f635d47485f\">เร็วๆ นี้</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"08c6c5c4-d7ac-40ea-95ba-700657d1d0e5\">สถาบันการเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"0643a35d-e503-4ccc-9482-72fd47031a60\">บริการธนาคารและการเงิน</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"0330532d-8c22-4f48-9cbd-74247b4bad06\">เร็วๆ นี้</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"a2961257-ce66-49d0-824e-68aed660c574\">ภาษี</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"738b8a26-4b6a-4495-9f5e-59af0af4e643\">การชำระภาษีของรัฐบาล</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"1be994ad-d1a8-4321-a168-c88394272d25\">เร็วๆ นี้</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"31197f7e-7b16-4627-9716-e1b5aa933c66\">ทำไมต้อง Xendit Bill Payments?</h3><ul data-block-id=\"97ddb4ff-b657-4191-b82a-5dbf6e4bd5e9\"><li data-block-id=\"ff1e12b3-66c4-41d4-8326-639da47aa457\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"678c2e8f-df1f-462e-8d26-787f7b9b5fb8\"><strong>การเชื่อมต่อเดียว ครอบคลุมทั่วภูมิภาค</strong>: การเชื่อมต่อเพียงครั้งเดียวสำหรับการชำระบิลในหลายประเทศ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c376d33a-b16a-4fc5-b15e-792162cb4b14\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"67035966-5d10-4ac4-a885-d81fdeae2c2c\"><strong>เงื่อนไขทางการค้าที่น่าสนใจ</strong>: ดำเนินการชำระบิลและรวบรวมเงินผ่านวิธีการชำระเงินของ Xendit โดยไม่มีค่าธรรมเนียมการรวบรวมการชำระเงิน (สำหรับวิธีการชำระเงินที่เลือก) พร้อมด้วยรายได้จากการชำระบิล</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bbb4cf3c-1e5f-4f3e-b71e-7ec0a74c265c\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"d873ddb0-a914-40c0-a2fb-fb81b0ac13e5\"><strong>ใช้ประโยชน์จากระบบนิเวศของ Xendit</strong>: เข้าถึงคุณสมบัติที่ครอบคลุมจากระบบนิเวศเกตเวย์การชำระเงินของ Xendit - การรายงานแบบรวมศูนย์, การออกบิล, การแจ้งเตือนทันที, และความเสถียรที่เชื่อถือได้พร้อมการสนับสนุนตลอด 24 ชั่วโมงทุกวัน</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"5fd9c6c0-3ef2-405b-bf03-e857820e4109\"></p>","SeoTitle":"ภาพรวม","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Generalidades","Slug":"product-overview-3","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><blockquote style=\"background:#fdf2ce;border-left:4px solid #7f6416;overflow:auto;\" data-block-id=\"mdirszr6-8n1saa-005\" class=\"warningBox\" data-background=\"#fdf2ce\" data-border=\"#7f6416\"><div class=\"blockquote-title\"><p data-block-id=\"mdirt4ou-nly321-008\">Aviso de Característica Piloto</p></div><p data-block-id=\"mdirszr6-b183yr-006\">El Bill Payments se encuentra actualmente en fase piloto.</p></blockquote><p data-block-id=\"e355563b-e19e-4c1c-80ec-31ea14969926\"><strong>Xendit Bill Payments</strong> permite a los comercios facilitar varios servicios de pago de facturas a través de una única integración de API. Este servicio permite a sus usuarios finales pagar facturas de servicios públicos, comprar servicios prepagados y realizar pagos regulares, todo dentro de su aplicación o plataforma.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"d5a7bc10-5e7f-4575-a146-666448954687\">¿Qué son los Bill Payments?</h3><p data-block-id=\"0e253919-5bf3-4f30-b26e-e617db79c51c\">Bill Payments es un servicio digital que permite a las personas pagar sus facturas y realizar compras electrónicamente. Piense en ello como un mostrador de pago digital donde sus usuarios pueden gestionar múltiples tipos de pagos en un solo lugar. En Indonesia, este servicio se conoce comúnmente como PPOB (Payment Point Online Banks).</p><p data-block-id=\"08eec1ed-f17e-4349-b5be-084e758e6c7f\"><strong>Características Comunes</strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"892ca4b8-0995-4b79-8cdc-1f6cfc4c83dd\"><li data-block-id=\"8e0885c2-e8be-417f-813c-86bb8209f844\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"ef000aef-809f-4234-b733-23bdd0c715f6\"><strong>Pagar Facturas de Servicios Públicos</strong>: Electricidad, agua y otros servicios públicos</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bb216e52-6dac-4f3b-b316-557a1c28c3d8\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"84aa5af5-c20c-45bd-a2cf-276fc6cdde86\"><strong>Comprar Servicios Prepagados</strong>: Recargas de crédito telefónico, tokens de electricidad, paquetes de datos de internet</p></li><li data-block-id=\"7a9f3949-714d-4514-b364-e294d291e051\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"d7c92c39-3a9b-42f2-931f-9d7a2499b676\"><strong>Realizar Pagos Regulares</strong>: Impuestos gubernamentales, primas de seguros, cuotas escolares</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"7a62ca4a-2b73-4b14-b6ca-399c79ab598a\">¿Cómo Funciona?</h3><p data-block-id=\"f1508a12-be8c-417b-ba72-884bb5c1cc77\"><img data-block-id=\"765f1b01-65ef-46fe-b08e-a8faa7792fe6\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(114).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><ol data-block-id=\"d537cd1e-aba3-4f19-b070-15b13c58555e\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"af2e3eb2-2f22-475b-b286-f978287d36eb\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"acabeba6-b7cf-439c-8b8d-4be3bcc6b50c\"><strong>El Cliente proporciona la información de la Cuenta</strong> - El usuario ingresa su número de cuenta (como el ID de cliente de electricidad)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"49124d39-f114-4335-aaca-fcc97f2a811f\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f5e3de3d-a30b-442e-b2bb-ad52ec5fbb6e\"><strong>El Sistema verifica los detalles de la Factura</strong> - Xendit verifica la cuenta y obtiene la información de la factura</p></li><li data-block-id=\"24a47bef-283b-4070-bcee-1e39e1329377\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"f8ac4a70-b540-4b56-8e81-e98a7548f1f0\"><strong>El Cliente confirma y paga</strong> - El usuario revisa los detalles de la factura y completa el pago</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bfd8dfa5-3c9c-4071-b5b3-3f54a3a24eb3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"300de6cf-9e95-4e68-96ee-e868ce46a04d\"><strong>El Pago es Procesado</strong> - La Transacción se ejecuta inmediatamente</p></li><li data-block-id=\"98013e39-c4f4-4b24-a43b-8d8cd88dc9e3\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"247409b0-2707-46ae-8ede-1800278e4937\"><strong>El Cliente recibe la Notificación</strong> - Se envía la Confirmación de Pago Exitoso</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"a88aa077-770f-4ec4-89c4-5f69f5a2e063\">En lugar de visitar múltiples oficinas de servicio para pagar diferentes facturas, sus usuarios pueden completar todos sus pagos a través de su plataforma con Xendit Bill Payments.</p><h3 data-block-id=\"70035706-df2a-4648-a9c6-49b97f2392c4\">Productos Compatibles</h3><p data-block-id=\"2523c633-4f53-4556-b0f0-de57ba7c9596\">Actualmente, Xendit Bill Payments es compatible con:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"912\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:912px;width:912px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:304px;\"><col style=\"width:304px;\"><col style=\"width:304px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"2d80a402-be6b-44b9-b9a1-d3b578df5cff\">Categoría</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"ff24f8e2-2094-419a-9b04-b93a0336caf5\">Productos</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"2df2fda0-f2c3-4219-aadc-e0b6d88e0cec\">Estado</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"d057440e-d73c-4875-b54e-6da9513fb970\">Servicios Públicos</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"50c9bda5-faad-4a8b-b73a-e34d957365ab\">Electricidad - PLN</p><ul data-block-id=\"e2f87cb3-f66a-4667-95ed-0d074bdc38c2\"><li data-block-id=\"0745468d-7ea5-441b-96fb-6e8791a234a4\"><p data-block-id=\"42887853-e5b1-4fce-81bb-9d0675c1d5ea\">Prepago</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c6310c51-1b26-4afa-95ef-192d351c38cf\"><p data-block-id=\"5b365676-68ac-4650-a02a-e8c65662f646\">Pospago</p></li></ul></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"94137d3f-16d3-4e80-9b9b-ae73ef6ddd1d\">Disponible</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"049d61dc-855e-4096-ac1f-f2377a5a2583\">Agua</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"44a2dd23-d923-4c37-a1a9-83c70173f0c3\">Varios PDAMs</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"37470440-a494-4576-bfeb-3e4d135a07bb\">Próximamente</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"00cd7eb9-134e-4c34-a4b2-60190ae6ec13\">Telco</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"8a948477-a272-433a-afd6-80e5bf7d4477\">Proveedores de teléfono e internet</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"faaf541a-5818-4637-a951-e856d9107093\">Próximamente</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"5e5938e4-88c9-4984-a5b4-7a85c418e086\">Entretenimiento</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"deacdcff-8df5-4711-900d-22a9972fc5da\">Servicios de streaming y contenido</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"5b3faff2-adab-46a5-be43-0f635d47485f\">Próximamente</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"08c6c5c4-d7ac-40ea-95ba-700657d1d0e5\">Instituciones Financieras</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"0643a35d-e503-4ccc-9482-72fd47031a60\">Servicios bancarios y financieros</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"0330532d-8c22-4f48-9cbd-74247b4bad06\">Próximamente</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"a2961257-ce66-49d0-824e-68aed660c574\">Impuestos</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"738b8a26-4b6a-4495-9f5e-59af0af4e643\">Pagos de impuestos gubernamentales</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"304\"><p data-block-id=\"1be994ad-d1a8-4321-a168-c88394272d25\">Próximamente</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h3 data-block-id=\"31197f7e-7b16-4627-9716-e1b5aa933c66\">¿Por qué Xendit Bill Payments?</h3><ul data-block-id=\"97ddb4ff-b657-4191-b82a-5dbf6e4bd5e9\"><li data-block-id=\"ff1e12b3-66c4-41d4-8326-639da47aa457\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"678c2e8f-df1f-462e-8d26-787f7b9b5fb8\"><strong>Una Sola Integración, Alcance Regional</strong>: Una única integración para pagos de facturas en varios países.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"c376d33a-b16a-4fc5-b15e-792162cb4b14\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"67035966-5d10-4ac4-a885-d81fdeae2c2c\"><strong>Términos Comerciales Atractivos</strong>: Procese pagos de facturas y cobre fondos a través de los métodos de pago de Xendit con cero tarifas de cobro de pagos (para métodos de pago seleccionados), complementado con ingresos por pagos de facturas.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"bbb4cf3c-1e5f-4f3e-b71e-7ec0a74c265c\" style=\"--pseudoBefore--fontWeight:bold\"><p data-block-id=\"d873ddb0-a914-40c0-a2fb-fb81b0ac13e5\"><strong>Aproveche el Ecosistema de Xendit</strong>: Acceda a características integrales del ecosistema de la pasarela de pago de Xendit: informes unificados, facturación, notificaciones instantáneas y tiempo de actividad confiable respaldado por soporte 24/7.</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"5fd9c6c0-3ef2-405b-bf03-e857820e4109\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Generalidades","Description":null}]